Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.08,0:00:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[dramatic music]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.13,0:00:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.74,0:01:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[ominous music]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.79,0:01:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- [in Japanese]\N- Any problems in the bedroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.55,0:01:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.68,0:01:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn your head\Nand cough, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.48,0:01:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.61,0:01:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please lie on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.74,0:02:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now flex.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Now lie on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This may feel a little cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As always, no alcohol,\Ntobacco, red meat, stress...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.36,0:02:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[lighter clicks]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:03:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[tense music]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- [in Japanese]\N- Sugita isn't scheduled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He says it's pressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Tozawa-san
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,in light of recent events
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps we would all benefit\Nfrom a reconsideration
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,of our... business model.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of your exposure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As well as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[stammers]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.91,0:04:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall continue as we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I am grateful for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[dramatic music]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God, Joshua\NJacob Adelstein,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you have been holding out on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Philips says\Nyou once beat up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,some kid in his classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- [laughs]\N- Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're right. He sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to graduate\Nhigh school knowing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing about chemistry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And Mom's, like,\Nseriously freaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please call her more, or\NI'm gonna lose my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.97,0:05:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She's, like, batshit crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:06:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, you... you smashed\Nthis kid's face into his desk?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do Mom and Dad know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[dog barking]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Arigato gozaimasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[doorbell rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- [in Japanese]\N- Tengu! Tengu! A Tengu is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Natchan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. I am often\Nmistaken for a goblin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:07:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,May I speak with\NDetective Katagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be difficult,\NMr... Adelstein,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,as my husband is not home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But I will tell him you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you expect him soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize if you\Nhave traveled far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, take the ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsumi! Ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And the beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[door slides open]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[in English] Beer and sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The "Meicho" told you this\Nis how you recruit a cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just hoping that it\Nwould get me through the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night, when you\Nconvinced that guy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,just to hand over his gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,what'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.25,0:08:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's complicated.\N- Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there... is there anything\Nelse that you can give me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- Give you?\N- Yeah, I didn't write anything
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,about the other\Nnight, like you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I helped you. Now\Ncan you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- It is late.\N- Thank you for the beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you really\Nwant, Mr. Adelstein?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[in Japanese] I want to\Nlearn how this city...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's beneath the\Nsurface... how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:09:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I can write what\Nis actually happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But right now, I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I don't\Nknow what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"A path opens to\Nthose who are honest."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound like my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A cop?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A coroner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I have known some good coroners.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[in English] At the\Nbar, what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Off the record.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The roots of the\Nyakuza run so deep,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,we can never get rid of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,so cops are encouraged\Nto maintain peace
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,among the different gangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokyo has been stable\Nthese last few years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But now Shinzo Tozawa and\Nhis men have come from Kansai
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,to try and claim a\Nlocal gang's territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A low-level move on\NChihara-kai turf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But you didn't tell the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so they can pretend\Nit didn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they don't retaliate,\Nand peace can hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm the one who\Nkept the peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[both laugh]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[in Japanese] Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Listen up! Polina, do\Nthat thing you do, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Frog jump jump, three jump jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,altogether jump jump,\Nsix jump jump...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[all cheer]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Polina! You're better\Nat it that we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- Excuse me.\N- Samantha-san, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hai. Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- [in English]\N- Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- [in Japanese]\N- New customer. Wants you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.31,0:11:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[speaking Japanese]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[speaking Japanese]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.66,0:11:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[in English] And a very\Ngood evening to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're trying to impress me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,mission accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Samantha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuo. A pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:11:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Matsuo Basho?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Basho?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- [in Japanese]\N- You kindle the fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll show you\Nsomething wonderful...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,a big ball of snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[in Japanese] "Sick on\Na journey, in my dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,staggering over\Nwithered fields."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And he was dying\Nwhen he wrote that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To old poets...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[tense music]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[siren wailing]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughter, indistinct chatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- [in Japanese]\N- This is your turf war.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Who pays for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Who told you to\Nserve Tozawa guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You expect me to\Nask the customers
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:13:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,which gang they belong to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I called you when\Nthey wouldn't pay,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and then your guys\Nwrecked my bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oyabun says he'll give you a\Nmonth's protection for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Protection like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't rely on Chihara-kai,\Nmaybe I should ask Tozawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Who told you to hit him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he was going\Nto switch to Tozawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That was negotiating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That asshole would never switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows I'd kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You having trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, with what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,With this. What we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.49,0:13:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been off lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember when I found you\Nin that arcade in Meguro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:14:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You stank like fish guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Working sixteen hour days,\Nyour life decided for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Like every other\Nsucker in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And what'd I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I set you free, little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to go\Nback, say the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And what happened\Nthere in the bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a time for talking\Nand a time for fists.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn to know the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Read the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Control yourself. Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, we'll do the\Npachinko place now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[dramatic music]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.01,0:14:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[indistinct chatter,\Nphone rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[English translation]\NMan sets himself on fire
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,with gasoline.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[in English] So many suicides.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seems like they're\Nall done in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why?\N- So the landlord does not
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,sue your family if you\Nburn his building down
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,when you set yourself on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- Seriously?\N- It happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fucking wack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wack?\N- Uh, bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Wack" means bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes.\N- [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- Get it?\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- [in Japanese]\N- Meicho Shimbun. City Desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My paper wasn't delivered today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's in charge over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I am very sorry. What address?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- What are you, a gaijin?\N- Put your supervisor on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Maruyama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How may I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman now? After the gaijin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Put a real employee on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Women and gaijin are all\Nwe have today. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[in English] I need you to\Ngo through these scrapbooks
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,for the last three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Find me any articles\Nabout single women
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,murdered by... [phone rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Meicho Shimbun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[in Japanese] One moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Adelstein.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[in Japanese] Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What address?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.34,0:16:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[exciting music]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:17:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[sirens wailing]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[in English] You stay\Nbehind me, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hear gunfire,\Nhit the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- [in Japanese]\N- Good morning, and thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Makabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[peppy music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[ominous music]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow us to make amends\Nfor the altercation
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakamura caused at\Nthe bar last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We are also sorry the\NChihara-kai man was stabbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is the man who\Nwielded the knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We have banished him\Nfrom the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.99,0:19:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the document of proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.83,0:19:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, your man\NNakamura owned the gun
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in violation of the Swords\Nand Firearms Control Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He did not, however,\Nown the bullets in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There were two bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So I will be arresting\Ntwo more men.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[indistinct chatter, laughter]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You got some balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Katagiri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's highly irregular.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What your men did was irregular.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Drawing guns, in\Na Chihara-kai bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Start a war with Ishida
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.33,0:20:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're starting one\Nwith me and the TMPD.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever Ishida is paying you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll double it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[tense music]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I regret giving\NNakamura a bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:21:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I am very regretful\Nof my actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We thank you for\Nyour cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[people clamoring,\Ncamera shutters clicking]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is totally harassment!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's right!\N- What are the charges?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.50,0:21:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.93,0:21:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have one of those?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No quotes from what\Nyou heard up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:21:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.48,0:21:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The raid, the\Narrests on suspicion
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.56,0:22:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,of firearm possession,\Ninvestigation is ongoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.69,0:22:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,An exclusive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.11,0:22:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[in English] With\Nmy compliments.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.12,0:22:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- [in Japanese]\N- One!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.25,0:22:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.79,0:22:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- The cops took three!\N- [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.67,0:22:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, they went for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.13,0:22:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[tense music]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.47,0:22:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.61,0:22:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.86,0:22:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,One beer, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.99,0:22:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:22:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- [in English]\N- Read it and weep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.00,0:23:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not bad work.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.12,0:23:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.67,0:23:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[in Japanese] "Gunshots\Nin Kabukicho bar,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.63,0:23:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"three Tozawa-gumi men arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.13,0:23:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"Around 1:14 a.m.\Non October 4th,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.72,0:23:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the Shinjuku Police... ".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.68,0:23:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. We get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.93,0:23:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.02,0:23:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Jake's scoop got published.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.98,0:23:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.52,0:23:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[in English] How did you get\Nto go along with these police
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.23,0:23:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,on an office raid of Tozawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.28,0:23:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the thing, Tin-Tin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.24,0:23:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop calling me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.20,0:23:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we stop calling him that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- No. We should not.\N- [laughter]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.33,0:23:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what Baku\Nsaid to me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.21,0:23:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Even the gaijin\Nwrites better than you,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.13,0:23:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and he is half-ape, half-Jew."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.59,0:23:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a fucking\Nliterature major.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.38,0:23:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, I'm full Jew, but
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.89,0:23:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you're a great writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.51,0:24:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A really good writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.18,0:24:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- [speaking Japanese]\N- So...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.69,0:24:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,fuck Baku.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.73,0:24:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck Baku.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.65,0:24:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- [in Japanese]\N- I endorse that sentiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.45,0:24:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful, man, that\Nglass is cracked.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.16,0:24:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[coughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.32,0:24:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You hit it too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.58,0:24:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- [laughs]\N- Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.25,0:24:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls, thank you for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.54,0:24:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we sell?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.75,0:24:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.92,0:24:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we sell liquor?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.09,0:24:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, ladies, we sell dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.59,0:24:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You go sell dreams. I'll sell\Nliquor and make commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.93,0:24:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.64,0:24:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Number one this week,\Nas usual, is Luna.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.77,0:24:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Show off!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.48,0:24:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us your secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.44,0:24:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[in English] Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.78,0:24:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[in Japanese] Samantha\Nis number two.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.99,0:24:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.82,0:24:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They understand how\Nto sell a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.41,0:25:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[in English] Unlike some of you
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.58,0:25:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,as we can all see by\Nthis skinny envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.29,0:25:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No table requests,\Nno away-dates,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.26,0:25:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,because you have the\Ngrace of a peasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.97,0:25:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You stink of desperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.64,0:25:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.18,0:25:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.02,0:25:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Polina.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.15,0:25:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate him. I hate that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.99,0:25:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.66,0:25:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he still doing this shit?\NHas he done anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.17,0:25:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I do what he wants, or I'm gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.38,0:25:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- Then fuck him.\N- Go do something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.59,0:25:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.34,0:25:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no degree, no experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.05,0:25:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My visa expired.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.34,0:26:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And my family needs money.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.05,0:26:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And I am their money.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.77,0:26:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- Without this job...\N- Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.18,0:26:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you're gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.27,0:26:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you. Tell me next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.40,0:26:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.95,0:26:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.21,0:26:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna start my own club.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.13,0:26:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I have money saved,\Nbut I can only...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.75,0:26:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only bring a few girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.13,0:26:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me. Tell no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.23,0:26:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[speaking Japanese]
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.90,0:26:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this Dolce & Gabbana?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.90,0:26:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Who fucking cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.07,0:26:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- [in English] Look, Malee.\N- Some dresses fell off a truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.95,0:27:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'll buy you one.\N- Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.82,0:27:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.41,0:27:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[in Japanese] I'm not\Npaying that much for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.25,0:27:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Prices are non-negotiable.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.66,0:27:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't pay a fucking thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.79,0:27:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, bitch, you\Npay what we say.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.96,0:27:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.30,0:27:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.76,0:27:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Treat these ladies with respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.59,0:27:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't talk to\Nme like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.09,0:27:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Unhappy girls means\Nunhappy clients
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.80,0:27:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,means less money\Nkicked up to Oyabun.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.85,0:27:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that's fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.93,0:27:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So shut the fuck up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.98,0:27:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.81,0:27:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ladies, our apologies.\N- Prices will be reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.24,0:27:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[soft indistinct\Nchatter, laughter]
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.53,0:27:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[in English] None\Nare right for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.50,0:27:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you know my style?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.21,0:27:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what will look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.13,0:27:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.33,0:28:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Try it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.34,0:28:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[dramatic music]
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.39,0:28:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.64,0:29:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.23,0:29:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sold. I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.24,0:29:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.99,0:29:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it off, and bring it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.08,0:29:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[ominous music]
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.08,0:29:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.83,0:30:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[scoffs]
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.59,0:30:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughter, indistinct chatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.18,0:30:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[speaking Japanese]
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.68,0:30:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me to\Nhost club tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.98,0:30:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm gonna go home.\N- Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.61,0:30:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.61,0:30:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want me to be happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.28,0:30:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.16,0:30:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine.
