Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.85,0:44:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He was being threatened.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.14,0:44:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[in Japanese] "Isn't your\Nfamily ashamed of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.02,0:44:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you dead?"
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.86,0:44:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[in English] Another man was\Nstabbed for the same reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.48,0:45:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A loan-sharking business, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.19,0:45:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I cannot pursue it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.41,0:45:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why?\N- It's
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.28,0:45:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- complicated.\N- Complicated?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.33,0:45:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- It is yakuza business.\N- I figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.66,0:45:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But which family or group\Nwithin that family...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.33,0:45:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost impossible to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.21,0:45:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.88,0:45:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This logo. It's smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.18,0:45:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,These companies\Nmove constantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.01,0:45:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Change numbers, open\Nand close their stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.77,0:45:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So by the time a cop or\Nreporter finds an address...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.27,0:45:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.02,0:45:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.65,0:45:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[in Japanese] So\Nhow do we find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.99,0:45:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And get them?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.04,0:45:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All companies get a\Nregistration number
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.50,0:45:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,when they're established.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.42,0:45:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many\Ntimes a company moves,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.79,0:46:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that number doesn't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.88,0:46:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The registration number.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.92,0:46:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,With this you could dig\Nuntil you found the man
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.51,0:46:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,who started it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.01,0:46:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[in English] I can be fired
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.39,0:46:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,if I share evidence\Nwith a reporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.89,0:46:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.23,0:46:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to put my\Ndaughters to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.21,0:46:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[in Japanese] Hey, tengu!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.08,0:46:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.92,0:46:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When my father was out, I\Nremoved this from his drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.34,0:46:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So he has not breached the\NNational Public Service Act.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.22,0:46:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But I am very ashamed!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.73,0:47:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.32,0:47:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.94,0:47:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[exciting music]
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.78,0:47:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[indistinct announcement\Nover P.A. system]
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.66,0:47:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.63,0:47:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[English translation]\NDIE DIE DIE DIE DIE
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.11,0:47:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[water running]
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.07,0:47:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,May I leave a message\Nfor him, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.28,0:47:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.32,0:47:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can meet Detective\NSoma anywhere, anytime,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.37,0:48:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,at his convenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.16,0:48:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- [in Korean]\N- When is fucking dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.25,0:48:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- [in Korean]\N- Five minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.67,0:48:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[in Japanese] Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.38,0:48:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Ah, hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.55,0:48:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Emi Maruyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.01,0:48:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.51,0:48:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.01,0:48:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[in Korean] Don't raise your\Nvoice when I'm on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.69,0:48:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- [in English]\N- And then what did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.77,0:48:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God. No, I\Nhad an awful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.07,0:48:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was with a realtor\Nfor five fucking hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.74,0:48:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,up and down stairs\Nall over Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.20,0:48:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.03,0:48:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and you won't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.70,0:48:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They say I have to\Nhave a guarantor.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.46,0:48:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Pol, did you borrow\Nmy... oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.54,0:48:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it. Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.37,0:48:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.13,0:48:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A guarantor... uh, a man to say
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.55,0:48:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm good for\Nit to the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.55,0:48:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no, I'll be there soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.26,0:48:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep an eye on Malee for\Nme. Ciao, Polina bella.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.89,0:49:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[camera shutter clicking]
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.44,0:49:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[tense music]
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.06,0:49:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[train rumbling]
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.04,0:49:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[ominous music]
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.08,0:49:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.18,0:49:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[indistinct chatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.78,0:49:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[soft music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.20,0:49:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[in Japanese] Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.53,0:49:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,For two.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.99,0:49:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- Two?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.16,0:50:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- All right.\N- Two beers, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.79,0:50:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay.\N- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.50,0:50:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[door clicks shut]
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.67,0:50:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[footsteps tapping]
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.34,0:50:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.63,0:50:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.30,0:50:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[in English] Everything all\Nright back there with that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.35,0:50:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Which guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.31,0:50:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In the alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.65,0:50:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- [in Japanese]\N- You're mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.36,0:50:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.40,0:50:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- [speaking Japanese]\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.62,0:50:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[in Japanese] Where's Tin-Tin?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.17,0:50:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- [in English] Running late.\N- He'll meet us at the cages.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.17,0:50:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I got something I\Nwant to show you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.67,0:50:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.01,0:50:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[in Japanese] Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.51,0:51:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- [laughter]\N- Pfft!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.60,0:51:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- [in English]\N- Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.02,0:51:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- [laughs]\N- Okay, okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.89,0:51:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts] Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.77,0:51:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[in Japanese] I'm expecting\Nmore out of you, American.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.19,0:51:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.94,0:51:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts] Pss!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.53,0:51:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.40,0:51:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- Pfft!\N- [laughter]
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.78,0:51:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts] [laughter]
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.87,0:51:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[in English] No,\Nthe question is...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.04,0:51:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is, who's the\Nperson behind these
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.45,0:51:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,scumbag loan-shark companies?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.83,0:51:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think it might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.38,0:51:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know, but\NI think that we have
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.17,0:51:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,enough information\Nin that folder
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.46,0:51:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to give us a pretty good lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.26,0:51:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You could play for\Nthe Hanshin Tigers.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.76,0:51:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.72,0:51:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- [in Japanese]\N- You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.90,0:52:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- [grunts]\N- Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.74,0:52:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[in English] Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.74,0:52:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.75,0:52:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- [grunts]\N- Jesus, you ever miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.29,0:52:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of\NAmerican loves yakuza
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.59,0:52:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but doesn't know\Nhow to swing a bat?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.67,0:52:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[horns honking]
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.72,0:52:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[tense music]
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.10,0:52:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- [in Japanese]\N- Two more swings and it's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.31,0:52:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Not interested.\N- Baseball is prosaic.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.60,0:52:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.27,0:52:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[in English] You're\Nplaying. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.81,0:52:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[in Japanese] No.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.90,0:52:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.28,0:52:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[in English] He doesn't\Nknow how to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.53,0:52:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, you don't.\N- No, come on, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.32,0:52:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't be a party pooper.\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.28,0:52:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- [in Japanese]\N- Who is Aderu-stein?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.79,0:52:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No one here with that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.38,0:52:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.80,0:53:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[in English] I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.55,0:53:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[in Japanese] We're\Ngonna take a drive. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.30,0:53:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[in English] I'm telling\Nyou, I don't speak Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.97,0:53:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[in Japanese] We told\Nyou to come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.80,0:53:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the fuck are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.97,0:53:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa, whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.93,0:53:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[in Japanese] Okay! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.47,0:53:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll come!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.73,0:53:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.81,0:53:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.31,0:53:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My jacket...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.98,0:53:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- [in English] You okay?\N- I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.40,0:53:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[speaking indistinctly]
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.99,0:53:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- [in Japanese]\N- Don't follow us.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.24,0:53:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
